The paper focuses on generating image descriptions using a combination of deep recurrent neural networks and convolutional neural networks, which are commonly used in computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, the paper also involves language modeling and generation, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of deep learning techniques and probability distributions also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.MM (Multimedia).
